&lt;li&gt;Own and optimize the organization’s Salesforce ecosystem, including Sales Cloud, CPQ, and Pardot (Marketing Cloud Account Engagement), ensuring scalable support for demand generation, lead lifecycle management, and revenue operations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
