&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement scalable Salesforce solutions using flows, automation, validation rules, and AI-driven capabilities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage integrations across the MarTech ecosystem to ensure seamless lead flow, campaign tracking, data integrity, and cross-platform interoperability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to improve operational efficiency, forecasting, and business scalability through automation and emerging AI technologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
