&lt;li&gt;Deep hands-on experience with Salesforce and Pardot configuration and automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Sales Cloud and repo

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title: &lt;/strong&gt;Senior Data Engineer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Department: &lt;/strong&gt;Product Development&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
